abstract_ssm: The Mulford family photograph collection, dating from circa 1880 to 1930, is housed in one glass plate negative box and one half manuscript box measuring 0.6 linear feet. The collection consists of 97 black-and-white glass plate negatives and film negatives and 93 black-and-white photographic prints.
